name: CASH GRAB
description:
CASH GRAB by Robote Games

Help MR. CASHMASTER PING PONG and collect ALL THE MONEY you can in 60 seconds. The winner takes it all! Level order is random, so you get a somewhat fresh adventure every time. Whoa.

CONTROLS: Arrows, ADW, Gamepad (Xbox and the likes)

Game design, graphics and code by Are (@juhapennanen)

Music and sounds by Aake (@robotemusic)

Made for #LOWREZJAM in 4 days
